# Soccer-AI Manual Testing Checklist

## Prerequisites
- [ ] Backend running on http://localhost:8000
- [ ] Frontend running on http://localhost:5173
- [ ] .env file has valid ANTHROPIC_API_KEY

## Startup Test
- [ ] Run `./start.sh` from soccer-AI/ directory
- [ ] Backend starts without errors
- [ ] Frontend starts without errors
- [ ] No port conflicts

---

## Backend API Tests

### Health Check
- [ ] GET http://localhost:8000/health returns {"status": "healthy"}

### Teams API
- [ ] GET /api/v1/teams returns list of 6 teams
- [ ] GET /api/v1/teams/42 returns Arsenal
- [ ] GET /api/v1/teams/42/legends returns legends array
- [ ] GET /api/v1/teams/42/rivalries returns rivalries array
- [ ] GET /api/v1/teams/42/moments returns moments array
- [ ] GET /api/v1/teams/42/personality returns full personality object

### Graph API
- [ ] GET /api/v1/graph returns nodes and edges
- [ ] GET /api/v1/graph/team/42 returns Arsenal subgraph
- [ ] Nodes have correct colors (red=team, orange=legend, blue=moment)

### Chat API
- [ ] POST /api/v1/chat with {"message": "Who is Arsenal's top scorer?"} returns response
- [ ] POST /api/v1/chat with {"message": "Tell me about the North London Derby", "club_id": "arsenal"} uses Arsenal persona

### KG Viewer
- [ ] GET /kg-viewer loads HTML page
- [ ] Graph renders with vis.js
- [ ] Team filter works
- [ ] Depth selector works
- [ ] Node click shows details

