## Frontend UI Tests

### Navigation
- [ ] Logo/Home link works
- [ ] Dashboard link works
- [ ] Teams link works
- [ ] Standings link works
- [ ] Chat link works

### Dashboard Page (/)
- [ ] Page loads without errors
- [ ] Stats cards display (or placeholders)
- [ ] Navigation works

### Teams Page (/teams)
- [ ] Team grid displays 6 teams
- [ ] Team cards show name, league
- [ ] Click team navigates to detail

### Team Detail Page (/teams/42)
- [ ] Team header shows name, stadium, manager
- [ ] Mood indicator appears (if mood data exists)
- [ ] Nickname appears in italics (if exists)

#### Overview Tab
- [ ] Fixtures section displays
- [ ] Results section displays
- [ ] GameCards render correctly

#### Legends Tab
- [ ] LegendsGrid displays
- [ ] Legend cards show name, position, era
- [ ] Goals/appearances show if available
- [ ] Star icons display

#### Rivalries Tab
- [ ] RivalryDisplay shows rivalries
- [ ] Intensity bars are colored correctly
- [ ] Derby names display
- [ ] Sorted by intensity (highest first)

#### Moments Tab
- [ ] MomentsTimeline displays
- [ ] Timeline line visible
- [ ] Emotion icons match emotion type
- [ ] Dates formatted correctly
- [ ] Sorted by date (recent first)

#### Graph Tab
- [ ] "Open Interactive Graph" button visible
- [ ] Click opens KG Viewer in new tab
- [ ] URL includes team parameter

### Standings Page (/standings)
- [ ] Table loads
- [ ] Teams sorted by position
- [ ] Stats display correctly

### Chat Page (/chat)
- [ ] Chat input visible
- [ ] Club selector works (Arsenal, Chelsea, Man Utd)
- [ ] Message sends successfully
- [ ] AI response appears
- [ ] Smart suggestions work

